text: Je Ne Sais Quoi is a song by Hera Björk from Iceland. She sang it in Eurovision Song Contest 2010. Je Ne Sais Quoi is French, and it means I don't know what. The song got to 19th place. ==Charts== Chart (2010) Peak position Iceland (RÚV) 2 Swiss Singles ChartSwiss Singles Chart 64 UK Singles ChartUK Singles Chart 131 == References == Category:2010 songs
